AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000600> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000600> "Primitive terms in a highest-level ontology such as BFO are terms which are so basic to our understanding of reality that there is no way of defining them in a non-circular fashion. For these, therefore, we can provide only elucidations, supplemented by examples and by axioms"@en)
